{"tid":2488073,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒：LG有望合作生產Apple Car 已接近簽約階段","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:25:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9113b9783d9dd3435e85420147a52629bf4d161a","tid":2488073,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕南韓大廠LG電子去年底傳出，計畫將部分電動車零組件業務分拆，與加拿大汽車零組件製造商麥格納（Magna International）合資創新企業，韓媒報導，這家合資公司近日與蘋果電動車的合作案「接近」談妥，有望簽約生產Apple Car。<br />\n<br />\n《韓國時報》報導，自從蘋果傳出將打造電動車後，各界就相當關注蘋果會與哪家工廠合作生產Apple Car，消息人士週二透露，暫時名為「LG Magna e-Powertrain」的合資公司已非常接近與蘋果簽約，預計將處理蘋果初期電動車生產，雙方目前仍在討論合約細節。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，考慮到LG集團旗下的LG顯示（LG Display）、LG化學（LG Chem）、LG能源解決方案（LG Energy Solution）和LG Innotek等子公司，都已在蘋果零件供應鏈內，因此蘋果不必擔心任何供應問題，LG集團也能保證電動車所需零件產量，並更快交貨。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3499163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3499163&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=30a661b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3499163&h=3f32e07d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3499163</a>"},{"pid":"0e763f4946127f0b38e3863407e764726bfbc3f2","tid":2488073,"uid":43369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"揸揸下燒底盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91e9465809d7641928ca9bf2c7316b04b628266","tid":2488073,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"車都有得險簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a886f6c691cee6f9f1bafc829e0c3078bf0d186d","tid":2488073,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"Apple 唔買tesla 而家又自己整apple car 係咪好on9?"},{"pid":"4582b2485b3735b9a3552c389db45